        "content": "The Cabinet Committee on Economic Affairs approved fresh coal linkages under a revamped **SHAKTI Policy** [7]. It introduces **Window–I for supplies at notified prices** and **Window–II for auction-based linkages at a premium**, streamlining allocation and boosting flexibility for Central Gencos, State Gencos, and Independent Power Producers [7]. Window–I continues existing nomination-based linkages for Central Sector TPPs and State Gencos [7]."
